(213, 1, '2014-07-28 18:07:20', '2014-07-28 18:07:20', '<p>Starting a program is easy. Once you have an idea, just click on the Start a Program link on our homepage under the heading “for teachers.” From this link, you will be asked a few questions that will better enable us to get things set up for you on our website. After you submit the information someone from the Corps Member Education Foundation will contact you for a follow up conversation. In most instances everything can be set up within one week of submitting your idea.Ready to start your program, <a href="http://www.cmef.org/user/register">click here</a>.</p>', 'How to Start a Program', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-start-a-program', '', '', '2014-08-01 16:21:02', '2014-08-01 16:21:02', '', 211, 'http://dev.pica.is/cmef/?page_id=213', 0, 'page', '', 0),
