(760, 41, '2015-01-09 17:05:52', '2015-01-09 17:05:52', '<p>\n	We have been training for 3 years to travel to Mars. The only thing we need now is enough money and a dependable space craft. These kids are really exited about the prospect of finding another planet to live on and bringing back the good news to their families. We know it''s a lofty goal but I think it''s attainable. The reward for donation will be a jar of sand from Mars and the chance to meet someone that has landed on Mars and made it back to tell the story.\n</p>', 'Send our class to Mars', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'send-our-class-to-mars', '', '', '2015-01-09 17:05:52', '2015-01-09 17:05:52', '', 0, 'http://dev.pica.is/cmef/?post_type=program&#038;p=760', 0, 'program', '', 0),
(761, 41, '2015-01-08 20:24:54', '2015-01-08 20:24:54', '<p>\n	   Our class has been training for this mission for 3 years. The  kids are healthy and ready for the journey to Mars. Their parents have all signed the permission slips all we need now is a worthy space craft to complete the mission. Please find it in your hearts to donate to this worthy cause. The amount is attainable so don’t be discouraged by all the zeros.\n</p>', 'Journey to Mars', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'journey-to-mars', '', '', '2015-01-08 20:31:54', '2015-01-08 20:31:54', '', 0, 'http://dev.pica.is/cmef/program/journey-to-mars/', 0, 'program', '', 0),
